{
  "script_id": "stats-basics",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "面对一大堆数据，我们常常想用一两个数字，就把它的特点说清楚。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "比如一次考试，全班几十个分数，老师最关心的往往是平均水平。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "统计学，就是教我们怎样从数据里提炼出这些关键信息。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "center",
      "line_id": "center-1",
      "filename": "center-center-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/center-center-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "第一类是集中趋势，描述数据大致聚在什么位置。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "center",
      "line_id": "center-2",
      "filename": "center-center-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/center-center-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "平均数，是把所有数加起来再除以个数，最常用也最直观。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "center",
      "line_id": "center-3",
      "filename": "center-center-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/center-center-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "中位数是排好序后正中间的那个数，众数则是出现次数最多的数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "spread",
      "line_id": "spread-1",
      "filename": "spread-spread-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/spread-spread-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "第二类是离散程度，描述数据是挤在一起，还是散得很开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "spread",
      "line_id": "spread-2",
      "filename": "spread-spread-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/spread-spread-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.6,
      "size": 25632,
      "text": "最简单的是极差，也就是最大值减最小值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "spread",
      "line_id": "spread-3",
      "filename": "spread-spread-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/spread-spread-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "更精细的是方差和标准差，它们衡量每个数偏离平均数的平均程度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.92,
      "size": 46656,
      "text": "换一组数据看看，红线是平均数，青线是中位数，它们的位置会随数据变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "当数据里出现一个特别大的值，平均数容易被拉高，中位数却更稳。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.77,
      "size": 44352,
      "text": "集中趋势用平均数、中位数、众数，告诉我们数据的中心在哪里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "离散程度用极差、方差、标准差，告诉我们数据有多分散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "stats-basics",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/stats-basics/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "选对统计量，才能读懂数据背后的故事，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 32.2,
  "total_size": 515232
}